(711, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">图3是“某区域地质剖面简图”，读图完成4～5题 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">4．图中甲乙丙三处的地质构造分别是 </span><img src="/tk/attached/image/20131230/20131230214556_81036.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="149" width="420" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A. 断层、向斜、背斜 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">B. 断层、背斜、向斜 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">C. 向斜、断层、背斜 </span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">D. 背斜、向斜、断层</span>\r\n</p>', '', '', 'B', '一般', '高考', 69, '', NULL, '\r\n	图3是“某区域地质剖面简图”，读图完成4～5题 \r\n\r\n\r\n	4．图中甲乙丙三处的地质构造分别是 \r\n\r\n\r\n	A. 断层、向斜、背斜 \r\n\r\n\r\n	B. 断层、背斜、向斜 \r\n\r\n\r\n	C. 向斜、断层、背斜 \r\n\r\n\r\n	D. 背斜、向斜、断层\r\n'),
