(1393, '<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">欧洲某企业在我国投资建立新厂，其产品主要出口欧洲，这一决策使得为其生产零部件的一些生产厂陆续迁至该厂附近。该企业设想：早晨接到订单，立即组织生产，下午发货，次日产品运到欧洲，据此，回答</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">48</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">～</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">50</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">题：</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">48</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．该厂产品可能是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．化工产品</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．电子产品</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．建筑陶瓷</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．生物药品</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'B', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	欧洲某企业在我国投资建立新厂，其产品主要出口欧洲，这一决策使得为其生产零部件的一些生产厂陆续迁至该厂附近。该企业设想：早晨接到订单，立即组织生产，下午发货，次日产品运到欧洲，据此，回答48～50题：\r\n\r\n\r\n	48．该厂产品可能是\r\n\r\n\r\n	　A．化工产品 　　 B．电子产品 　　 C．建筑陶瓷 　　 D．生物药品\r\n'),
(1394, '<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">49</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．该工厂布局首先考虑靠近</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．海港</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．航空港</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．公路枢纽</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．铁路枢纽</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'B', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	49．该工厂布局首先考虑靠近\r\n\r\n\r\n	　 A．海港 　 B．航空港 　　 C．公路枢纽 　 D．铁路枢纽\r\n'),
(1395, '<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">50</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．该企业还对我国为其生产零部件的厂家加以培育，这一过程称为</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．城市化</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．全球化</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．本地化</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">　　</span><span><span> </span></span><span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．工业化</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	50．该企业还对我国为其生产零部件的厂家加以培育，这一过程称为\r\n\r\n\r\n	　A．城市化 　　 B．全球化 　　 C．本地化 　　  D．工业化\r\n'),
(1396, '<p>\r\n	<span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">读</span><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><span style="font-size:16px;">我国正在实施的资源跨地区调配示意图</span><span style="font-size:16px;">”</span><span style="font-size:16px;">，完成</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">5</span><span style="font-size:16px;">1</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">～</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">53</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">题。</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0.5cm;text-indent:-0.5cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">51</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．箭头</span><span style="font-size:16px;">①</span><span style="font-size:16px;">和③的运输方式中具有共性的是</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、管道运输</span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、水陆联运</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095027_39997.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="188" width="217" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.37cm;">\r\n	<span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、高压输电</span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">、航空运输</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	读“我国正在实施的资源跨地区调配示意图”，完成51～53题。\r\n\r\n\r\n	51．箭头①和③的运输方式中具有共性的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A、管道运输 B、水陆联运 \r\n\r\n\r\n	 C、高压输电 D、航空运输\r\n'),
(1397, '<p style="margin-left:0.5cm;text-indent:-0.5cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">52</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．有专家指出，④工程很可能加重沿途有些地区土壤的次生盐碱化。有关成因的叙述正确的是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">①</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">沿途有些地区潜水面较低，河水渗漏补给地下水<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095124_60510.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="176" width="204" /></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.19cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">②</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">沿途有些地区土壤中的盐分有逐渐向地表积聚的可能</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.19cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">③</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">沿途地区城市生活污水的大量排放</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0.56cm;text-indent:-0.37cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">④</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">沿途地区主要地处半湿润地区，非雨季时段，蒸发量大于降水量</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="margin-left:0.56cm;text-indent:-0.37cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">⑤</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">沿途地区有大量海水的入侵</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">①②</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">④</span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、</span><span style="font-size:16px;">①</span><span style="font-size:16px;">③④</span><span> </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.37cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、③④⑤</span><span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">　</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、</span><span style="font-size:16px;">②</span><span style="font-size:16px;">③⑤</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'A', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	52．有专家指出，④工程很可能加重沿途有些地区土壤的次生盐碱化。有关成因的叙述正确的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	①沿途有些地区潜水面较低，河水渗漏补给地下水\r\n\r\n\r\n	②沿途有些地区土壤中的盐分有逐渐向地表积聚的可能\r\n\r\n\r\n	③沿途地区城市生活污水的大量排放\r\n\r\n\r\n	④沿途地区主要地处半湿润地区，非雨季时段，蒸发量大于降水量\r\n\r\n\r\n	⑤沿途地区有大量海水的入侵\r\n\r\n\r\n	A、①②④  B、①③④  \r\n\r\n\r\n	C、③④⑤ 　D、②③⑤\r\n');
INSERT INTO `dilixzts` (`id`, `xzttext`, `tu1url`, `tu2url`, `da`, `nanyidu`, `shitilexing`, `keshiid`, `jtsl`, `zhishidianid`, `xzt`) VALUES
(1398, '<p style="margin-left:0.5cm;text-indent:-0.5cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">53</span><span></span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">②</span><span style="font-size:16px;">工程对于我国能源开发与利用的意义是<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095233_71780.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="174" width="201" /></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A </span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">缓解我国由于能源消费以石油为主所带来的环境压力</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">B </span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">根本上改变我国的能源结构，以气代煤</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">C </span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">可以实现</span><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><span style="font-size:16px;">东西部双赢</span><span style="font-size:16px;">”</span><span style="font-size:16px;">，根本上解决能源供应紧张的状况</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">D </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">促进沿线地区特别是长江三角洲地区大气环境的改善</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'D', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	53．②工程对于我国能源开发与利用的意义是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A 缓解我国由于能源消费以石油为主所带来的环境压力\r\n\r\n\r\n	B 根本上改变我国的能源结构，以气代煤\r\n\r\n\r\n	C 可以实现“东西部双赢”，根本上解决能源供应紧张的状况\r\n\r\n\r\n	 D 促进沿线地区特别是长江三角洲地区大气环境的改善\r\n'),
(1399, '<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">西部地区可开发的水能资源占全国的</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">72</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">％，己探明的煤炭保有储量占全国的</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">39</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">％，下图是西电东送示意图，据图回答</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">54</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">～</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">56</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">题。<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095330_11726.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="185" width="214" /></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">54</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送可以缓解东部日益严重的环保压</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">力，主要是因为</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送使电价升高，东部用电量减少 </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送使电价降低，使用环保电器者增多</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送使东部地区煤炭输入量减少 </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送使东部地区工业成本降低，</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:1.11cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">有能力改善环保条件</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	西部地区可开发的水能资源占全国的72％，己探明的煤炭保有储量占全国的39％，下图是西电东送示意图，据图回答54～56题。\r\n\r\n\r\n	54．西电东送可以缓解东部日益严重的环保压\r\n\r\n\r\n	力，主要是因为\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．西电东送使电价升高，东部用电量减少  \r\n\r\n\r\n	B．西电东送使电价降低，使用环保电器者增多\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．西电东送使东部地区煤炭输入量减少  \r\n\r\n\r\n	D．西电东送使东部地区工业成本降低，\r\n\r\n\r\n	有能力改善环保条件\r\n'),
(1400, '<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">55</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送是把西部地区的水电和坑口电站的电能输往东部，图中坑口电站分布较多的是</span><img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095410_45107.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="172" width="199" /></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">AB <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">CD <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">DE <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">AE</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'D', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	55．西电东送是把西部地区的水电和坑口电站的电能输往东部，图中坑口电站分布较多的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．AB \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	B．CD \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．DE \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	D．AE\r\n'),
(1401, '<p style="text-indent:0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">56</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．水能资源得到梯级开发的是<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095500_68023.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="172" width="199" /></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">AB</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"> B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">CE <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"> C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">AE <br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">BE</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'D', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	56．水能资源得到梯级开发的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．AB\r\n\r\n\r\n	 B．CE \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	 C．AE \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	 D．BE\r\n'),
(1402, '<p align="CENTER">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">产业重心是区域产业产值空间分布的重心。下图中，示意中国三次产业重心的经、纬度变化</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">(</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">不含台湾、香港、澳门的统计资料</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">)</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">。完成</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">57</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">～</span></span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">60</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">题。</span></span></span></span><span></span><img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095550_46484.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="125" width="333" />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">57</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．对三大产业叙述正确的是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.77cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第一产业是指农业和工业</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.77cm;">\r\n	<span><span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．服务业属于第二产业的范畴</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.77cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第三产业包括流通业和服务业</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.77cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．建筑业属第一产业</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	产业重心是区域产业产值空间分布的重心。下图中，示意中国三次产业重心的经、纬度变化(不含台湾、香港、澳门的统计资料)。完成57～60题。\r\n\r\n\r\n	57．对三大产业叙述正确的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．第一产业是指农业和工业\r\n\r\n\r\n	 B．服务业属于第二产业的范畴\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．第三产业包括流通业和服务业  \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	D．建筑业属第一产业\r\n'),
(1403, '<p>\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">58</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">图中</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">①</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">、</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">②</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">、</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">③</span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">线依次代表</span><img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095654_11812.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="117" width="312" /></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">第一产业、第二产业、第三产业</span><span><span><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">第二产业、第三产业、第一产业</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">第一产业、第三产业、第二产业</span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><br />\r\n</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">第三产业、第一产业、第二产业</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'B', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	58．图中①、②、③线依次代表\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．第一产业、第二产业、第三产业\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	  B．第二产业、第三产业、第一产业\r\n\r\n\r\n	 C．第一产业、第三产业、第二产业 \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	D．第三产业、第一产业、第二产业\r\n'),
(1404, '<p>\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">59</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．从产业重心的纬度变化看<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140107/20140107095749_95569.jpg" alt="" align="right" height="158" width="421" /></span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．三次产业重心均向北移动</span></span><span><span><br />\r\n</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第一产业重心移动最快</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第二产业重心移动最快</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"></span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第三产业重心移动最快</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	59．从产业重心的纬度变化看\r\n\r\n\r\n	 A．三次产业重心均向北移动\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n	 B．第一产业重心移动最快\r\n\r\n\r\n	  C．第二产业重心移动最快\r\n\r\n\r\n	  D．第三产业重心移动最快\r\n'),
(1405, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">60</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．自</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">1985</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">年至</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">2003</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">年，产业重心移动的趋势是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第二产业向东南</span></span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第二产业向东北</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第一产业向东南</span></span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．第三产业向东南</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'D', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	60．自1985年至2003年，产业重心移动的趋势是\r\n\r\n\r\n	 A．第二产业向东南 B．第二产业向东北\r\n\r\n\r\n	 C．第一产业向东南  D．第三产业向东南\r\n'),
(1406, '<p>\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">双选61</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．三峡电站成为我国最大电站的自然条件有&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.85cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．长江上游流量大且为唯一入海通道</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．我国西部大开发的需要</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.85cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．地势落差大&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．解决华东、华中能源的需要</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'AC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选61．三峡电站成为我国最大电站的自然条件有&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;  \r\n\r\n\r\n	A．长江上游流量大且为唯一入海通道&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; B．我国西部大开发的需要\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．地势落差大&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; D．解决华东、华中能源的需要\r\n'),
(1407, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选62</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．西电东送工程中，有关叙述错误的是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．送达地区为广东、华东地区和京津唐地区</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">南部通道主要输送的是水电，没有火电</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">中部通道输送的三峡和澜沧江的水电</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．北部通道是将黄河上中游的水电和山西、内蒙古坑口电站的电能输送出去</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'BC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选62．西电东送工程中，有关叙述错误的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．送达地区为广东、华东地区和京津唐地区\r\n\r\n\r\n	B．南部通道主要输送的是水电，没有火电\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．中部通道输送的三峡和澜沧江的水电\r\n\r\n\r\n	D．北部通道是将黄河上中游的水电和山西、内蒙古坑口电站的电能输送出去\r\n'),
(1408, '<p style="margin-left:0.56cm;text-indent:-0.56cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选63.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">我国台湾电子企业为了降低成本，提高国际竞争力，生产工厂大量西移至广东东莞等地，其考虑的因素是：</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">A.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">劳动成本 </span></span> </span><span> </span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">土地成本 </span></span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;"> C.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">科技成本 </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"> D.</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">原料成本</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'AB', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选63.我国台湾电子企业为了降低成本，提高国际竞争力，生产工厂大量西移至广东东莞等地，其考虑的因素是：\r\n\r\n\r\n	A.劳动成本   B.土地成本   C.科技成本  D.原料成本\r\n'),
(1409, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选64</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">20</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">世纪下半叶东亚劳动密集型产业转移的顺序正确的是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．日本——我国东部沿海地区</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">日本——韩国、我国台湾、香港地区</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">韩国、我国台湾、香港地区——我国东部沿海地区</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．韩国、我国台湾、香港地区——我国中西部地区</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'BC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选64．20世纪下半叶东亚劳动密集型产业转移的顺序正确的是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．日本——我国东部沿海地区\r\n\r\n\r\n	B．日本——韩国、我国台湾、香港地区\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．韩国、我国台湾、香港地区——我国东部沿海地区\r\n\r\n\r\n	D．韩国、我国台湾、香港地区——我国中西部地区\r\n'),
(1410, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选65</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．水资源跨区域调配对自然环境的影响有\r\n                            （     ）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．可以改变大范围的气候状况 </span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">可以保护濒危的野生动植物</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．可以减少地表水的使用 </span><span> </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">　　D</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">可以缓解受水区的生态缺水</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'BD', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选65．水资源跨区域调配对自然环境的影响有\r\n                            （     ）\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．可以改变大范围的气候状况  B．可以保护濒危的野生动植物\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．可以减少地表水的使用  　　D．可以缓解受水区的生态缺水\r\n'),
(1411, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">66</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．珠江三角洲地区工业化和城市化进一步推进的制约因素是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">、轻工业 </span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">、重工业 </span></span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">、旅游业 </span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">、机械制造业</span></span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'BD', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	66．珠江三角洲地区工业化和城市化进一步推进的制约因素是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A、轻工业  B、重工业  C、旅游业 D、机械制造业\r\n'),
(1412, '<p style="margin-left:0.74cm;text-indent:-0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">67</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．与长江三角洲和京津唐地区相比，目前珠江三角洲地区对外资的吸引力正在下降，工业化和城市化的后劲日显不足。原因是珠江三角洲地区的</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">产业基础处于劣势 </span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．劳动力资源不丰富 </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span></span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．</span><span style="font-size:16px;">国内的市场腹地小 </span> </span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．交通条件差</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'AC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	67．与长江三角洲和京津唐地区相比，目前珠江三角洲地区对外资的吸引力正在下降，工业化和城市化的后劲日显不足。原因是珠江三角洲地区的\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．产业基础处于劣势  B．劳动力资源不丰富  \r\n\r\n\r\n	C．国内的市场腹地小  D．交通条件差\r\n'),
(1413, '<p align="LEFT">\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选68</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．我国“西电东送”工程的重要意义是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.64cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．弥补东部地区电力消费的缺口&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．加速新疆的经济开发和农业的发展</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.64cm;" align="LEFT">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．减少东部地区的环境污染&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．全面改善西部地区的能源消费结构　</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'AC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选68．我国“西电东送”工程的重要意义是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．弥补东部地区电力消费的缺口&nbsp; B．加速新疆的经济开发和农业的发展\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．减少东部地区的环境污染&nbsp;&nbsp; D．全面改善西部地区的能源消费结构　\r\n'),
(1414, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选69</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．制约西部经济发展的两个主要因素是</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">．热量 </span><span> </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．水源 </span></span></span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．交通 </span></span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．地形</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'BC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选69．制约西部经济发展的两个主要因素是\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．热量  B．水源 C．交通  D．地形\r\n'),
(1415, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;">双选70</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．站在香港的角度，该地区企业要向内地迁移的原因有</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．香港地价较高 </span></span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．内地服务业发达</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="text-indent:0.74cm;">\r\n	<span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．内地工资水平较低 </span></span> </span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">．香港人数量剧减</span></span>\r\n</p>', NULL, NULL, 'AC', '一般', '', 100, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	双选70．站在香港的角度，该地区企业要向内地迁移的原因有\r\n\r\n\r\n	A．香港地价较高  B．内地服务业发达\r\n\r\n\r\n	C．内地工资水平较低  D．香港人数量剧减\r\n'),
(1416, '<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>1.上面四幅图中，正确表示冷锋天气的是(<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>) </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>A. a<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>B. b<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n</span></b></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b><span></span>C. c<span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>D. d</b></span>\r\n		</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<img src="/tk/attached/image/20140306/20140306151551_60160.gif" alt="" align="right" height="65" width="352" />', NULL, NULL, 'A', '一般', '', 105, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	\r\n		1.上面四幅图中，正确表示冷锋天气的是(&nbsp;&nbsp; ) \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		\r\n			A. a&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; B. b&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; \r\n\r\n		\r\n		\r\n			C. c&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; D. d\r\n		\r\n	\r\n\r\n'),
(1417, '<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>2.关于冷锋的叙述，正确的有(<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>) </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>A.是由冷气团主动移向暖气团形成的锋 </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>B.过境后气温和气压都骤降 </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>C.过境后会有雨雪天气 </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>D.快速移动的冷锋过境时多产生连续性降雨</b></span><span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:red;"><b> </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, 'A', '一般', '', 105, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	\r\n		2.关于冷锋的叙述，正确的有(&nbsp;&nbsp; ) \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		A.是由冷气团主动移向暖气团形成的锋 \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		B.过境后气温和气压都骤降 \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		C.过境后会有雨雪天气 \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		D.快速移动的冷锋过境时多产生连续性降雨 \r\n	\r\n'),
(1418, '<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>3.冷锋与暖锋的共同点是(<span>&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>) </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>A.都形成连续性降水 </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>B.降水都降在锋前 </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>C.都是冷气团在下，暖气团在上<span> </span> </b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span style="font-family:宋体;font-size:22pt;color:black;"><b>D.都属于气候系统</b></span>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>', NULL, NULL, 'C', '一般', '', 105, NULL, NULL, '\r\n	\r\n		3.冷锋与暖锋的共同点是(&nbsp;&nbsp; ) \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		A.都形成连续性降水 \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		B.降水都降在锋前 \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		C.都是冷气团在下，暖气团在上  \r\n	\r\n	\r\n		D.都属于气候系统\r\n	\r\n'),
