(9, 102, '<p>\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">探究一：\n读我国东部地区一般年份夏季风的进退情况示意图，</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><img src="/tk/attached/image/20131227/20131227082959_69025.png" alt="" align="right" height="265" width="180" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">回答下列问题。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">1</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">地区夏秋季节的降水类型是</span>＿＿＿<u><span></span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">雨和</span>＿＿＿<span> </span><u><span> </span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">雨。</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">2</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">地区每年</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">6</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">月一般会出现</span><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><u><span> </span></u>＿＿＿<span><span> </span></span><u><span> </span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">”</span><span style="font-size:16px;">天气。</span></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">3</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）图中</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">和</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">两地区，较易出现春旱的是</span><u><span> ＿＿＿</span></u></span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"></span><u> </u><span><span><span style="font-