(49, 102, '<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">读我国东部地区一般年份夏季风的进退情况示意图，</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><img src="/tk/attached/image/20140108/20140108090308_55839.png" alt="" height="265" width="180" align="right" /></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">回答下列问题。</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">1</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">A</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">地区夏秋季节的降水类型是</span>__<span><u><span> </span></u></span><u><span> </span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">雨和</span>___<span> </span><u><span> </span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">雨。</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">2</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">B</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">地区每年</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">6</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">月一般会出现</span><span style="font-size:16px;">“</span><u>____</u><span style="font-size:16px;"></span><span><span> </span></span><u><span> </span></u><span style="font-size:16px;">”</span><span style="font-size:16px;">天气。</span></span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">（</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">3</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">）图中</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">C</span><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:16px;">和</span></span><span style="font-size:16px;">D</span><span><span><span style="font-size:16px;">两地区，较易出现春旱的是</span><u><span> </span></u></span></span>__<